quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Iôqa Bu tgelda deg ufus iS, u Neppa, Izmer i yal cci"
  67,2,"i Ixelqen tameppant, tameddurt, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb: anwa degwen ara ixedmen igiten ilhan sennig wiyav. Neppa d Uzmir, Ipsemmiê"
  67,3,"i Ixelqen ûa igenwan d idurra. Deg wayen Ixleq Uênin, ur tepwaliv ayen ixuûûen. Ernu sikked ma a pwaliv i$isiyen"
  67,4,"Sinna, ger tiî ik berdayen. Iéôi a d iu$al $uôek, iêfa, u inzef"
  67,5,"Ni$ Ncebbeê igenni aqôib s teftilin, Nôeooem yisent cwaîen, Nhegga yasen aâaqeb n tmes"
  67,6,"I wid inekôen Mass nnsen, aâaqeb n Loahennama. A tu$alin tucmip"
  67,7,"Mi pwaveggôen $uôes, ad slen la tesraâriâ, u neppat trekkem"
  67,8,"Qôib a ppeftutes seg iûiv. Yal tikelt ara iwaveggeô $uôes urbaâ, a ten steqsin iâssasen is: \"aâni ur kwen id iusi ara uneddaô"
  67,9,"Ad inin: \"ih, iusa ya$ d uneddaô, nenkeô u nenna: ur illi ay d Issuder Öebbi, aql akwen kan di le$wlav meqqwôen"
  67,10,"U nnan: \"lemmer nelli nsell ne$ nfehhem, ur nelli seg wat tmes"
  67,11,Qaôôen s ibekkaven nnsen. Asêaq i at tmes
  67,12,"Wanag, i wid ippagwaden Mass nnsen, di tbavnit, ssmaê akked warraz meqqwôen"
  67,13,"Hedôet s sser ne$ âinani, ihi, Neppa Iéôa ayen illan deg idmaren"
  67,14,"Day ur Iéôi ara Win Ixelqen, Laîif Ippuxebbôen"
  67,15,"Neppa i wen Irran tamurt d tamvuât. Elêut deg ibraêen is, ççet si ôôeéq is. £uôeS tanekra"
  67,16,"Ma tepputebtem ar, Win Illan deg igenni, ad Irr tamurt a ppertem yiswen? Appan la teppembwiwil"
  67,17,"Ma tepputebtem, ar Win Illan deg igenni, awen d Iazen tabucivant n yid$a$en? D$a, a ppissinem anwa t unabi W"
  67,18,Ni$ nekôen imezwura nnsen. Amek d Zzi$ fellasen
  67,19,"Ahat ur walan ara ifôax, sennig sen, d idurra, afriwen ceôqen, ur côiqen. Siwa Aênin iten Iîfen. Neppa, ih, Issikkid yal cci"
  67,20,"Anwa wa ay d aâsekôiw nnwen, ara kwen isellken, war Aênin? Ijehliyen atnan kan di le$ôuô"
  67,21,"Anwa wa ara kwen iôeéqen ma Ijmaâ l$it iS? Maca, vellelen deg u$unfu akked leqbaêa"
  67,22,"Win iteddun, ibra i uqeôôu, day ipwanha sennig win iteddun, irfed aqeôôu, deg ubrid uwqim"
  67,23,"Ini: \"d Neppa ikwen id Ixelqen. Irra yawen timejjin, allen, ulawen. Drus ay tesnemmirem"
  67,24,"Ini: \"d Neppa ikwen isseftin di tmurt, ar $uôeS ara tepwafesrem"
  67,25,"La qqaôen: \"melmi lemâahda agi, ma d tidep ay tessawalem"
  67,26,"Ini: \"i Iéôan siwa Öebbi. Nek d aneddaô kan ipbegginen"
  67,27,"Mara a t walin iqeôb ed, ad ndellen wudmawen n wid ijehlen. A d inin: \"atan wayen tessuturem"
  67,28,"Ini: \"ma twalam ma In$a ya$ Öebbi, nek d imeddukwal iw, ne$ ma Iêun fella$? Ihi, anwa ara isellken ijehliyen seg uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  67,29,"Ini: \"Neppa d Aênin, syiS numen, fellaS neppkel. A ppeéôem anwa i illan di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  67,30,"Ini: \"ma twalam, lemmer ad zzren waman nnwen, w ar awen d iawin aman ippazalen"
  68,1,S wamru akked wayen pjerriden
  68,2,"Keçç, s l$it n Mass ik, ur telliv d aôehbani"
  68,3,"Ih, i keçç arraz ur nepnegzay"
  68,4,"Ih, keçç, lxaîeô ik d ûûam"
  68,5,"A pwaliv, ad walin"
  68,6,anwa degwen ippuhewwlen
  68,7,"D Mass ik, ih, i Izôan sennig wiyav, anwa iff$en abrid iS. D Neppa i Izôan, sennig wiyav, anwi ipwanhan"
  68,8,"Ihi, ur ppak awal i inekkaôen"
  68,9,"Ssaramen a ppestaâmlev, akken ad staâmlen"
  68,10,Ur ssemêas i yal afuêan ipgallan
  68,11,aqeôôad ileêêun iplemmim
  68,12,"i igelden lxiô, ippawven, idenben"
  68,13,"amjuô, u irna d akluc"
  68,14,"Xas $uôes ayla, igwerdan"
  68,15,"Ma $ôan as issekniyen nne£, iqqaô: \"d timucuha imezwura"
  68,16,A t Nweccem deg wanzaren
  68,17,"Ih, Njeôôeb iten akken Njeôôeb at leonan, mi gullen, ar di tûebêit, ad $elten"
  68,18,Ggulen ur êniten
  68,19,"Tezzi yas tbucivant s$uô Mass ik, nitni îîsen"
  68,20,Iu$al amzun d lbuô
  68,21,Di tûebêit msawalen
  68,22,"ekkret zik, ar lexla nnwen, ma a p$elltem"
  68,23,"Teddun, sbecbucen garasen"
  68,24,"igellil, assa, ur t ppaooat a p id ikçem\". ö"
  68,25,"Öuêen ppeklen, zemren"
  68,26,"Mi t walan, nnan: \"nekwni d im$eôôqen"
  68,27,"Ih, aql a$ nepwaêeôôem"
  68,28,"Inna uêdiq mavi nnsen: \"day ur awen nni$ ara: a lemmer tesbuccuâem"
  68,29,"Nnan: \"nesbuccaâ Mass nne$. Nella, s tidep, d imednas"
  68,30,"Mqabalen, ppemyuzzamen"
  68,31,"Nnan: \"a ssexv nne$, nella d imjuôen"
  68,32,"Ahat Mass nne$ ad a$ d I$ôem sennig waya; ih, nekwni, ar Mass nne$, d imectaqen"
  68,33,"Am akka, aqeîîi. Aqeîîi n laxeôt, war ccekk, meqqweô kteô, lemmer éôin"
  68,34,"Ih, i wid ipêezziben i Mass nnsen, Loennet n ssuâada"
  68,35,Aâni Nerr imvuâen am ibe$wviyen
  68,36,Acu ikwen iu$en? Amek tepêuddum
  68,37,Ne$ tesâam tazmamt ideg tlemdem
  68,38,"degs, i kunwi, s tidep, ayen tesmenyafem"
  68,39,"Ne$ $uôwen tuqqna s$uône$, ar ass iqeîîiten, ara kwen id ias wayen têuddem"
  68,40,"Steqsi ten ma, $ef waya, $uôsen îîamen"
  68,41,"ne$ $uôsen icriken? Ihi, a d awin icriken nnsen, ma d tidep ay ssawalen"
  68,42,"Ass ideg ara tepwafveê twa$it, ad asen inin ad knun, ur zmiren"
  68,43,"Ad brunt wallen, ddell iwwet iten. Ni$ pwanecden ar lekni, mi llan ûeêêan"
  68,44,"Eoo iyI akked wid iskaddben awal agi. Ad asen Ddu$ cwiî, cwiî, seg wanda ur éôin"
  68,45,Ad asen Fke$ lmudda. Ni$ tiêeôci W teéweô
  68,46,"Ne$ tessutrev taqdiât, fellasen d îîlaba ééayen"
  68,47,"Ne$ $uôsen tabavnit, d$a la pparun"
  68,48,"Eûbeô i ôôay n Mass ik, ur ppili am bu uslem, i d issawlen mi ippuêeyyeô"
  68,49,"Lemmer ur t id issukkes l$it n Mass is, a d iu$al ar lxali, d amaâfun"
  68,50,"Ifren it Mass is, Irra t seg iâaôviyen"
  68,51,"Qôib i k smalen ijehliyen, s wallen nnsen, mi slan i usmekti. La qqaôen: \"ar neppa d aôehbani"
  68,52,"Neppa, d asmekti kan i imavalen"
  69,1,Tin imuêeppmen
  69,2,D acu ay d tin imuêeppmen
  69,3,"W ar ak imlen d acu p, tin imuêeppmen"
  69,4,Tamud akked Âad skaddben tin ipôuéun
  69,5,Tamud pwan$an s termegt
  69,6,Âad pwan$an s uûeôûaô aqesêan
  69,7,"Iêeppem it, fellasen, ûa wavan, îam wussan, d imezgi. A pwaliv din imdanen seôâan, am ize$wôan n tezdayt iruzen"
  69,8,Twalav ma illa wacu d igwran segsen
  69,9,"Iusa d Ferâun akked wid i t id izwaren, akked tid ippin, s lfalîat"
  69,10,Âuûan amazan n Mass nnsen. Issemêalleq asen s lqewwa
  69,11,"Ih, aman asmi ccewcwen, Nebbwi kwen di lbabur"
  69,12,"iwakken ad awen t Nerr d asmekti, ad as ccfun imeééu$en isellen"
  69,13,"Ma ûuven di lbuq, aûuvu yiwen"
  69,14,"idurar akked swaêel ad pwarefden, yiwet n tiôéi ara ten iôéen"
  69,15,"Ass nni, a ppevôu tedyant"
  69,16,"Ad iceqqeq igenni, ad icerreg, assen"
  69,17,"Lmalayek, di leriaf is. Assen, di îam ad refdent, sennig sent, asgeld n Mass ik"
  69,18,"A ppepufesren, assen; iccer ur iteffer segwen"
  69,19,"Wanag win iwumi fkan tazmamt is, yeffus is, a d yini: \"atan, e$ôet adlis iw"
  69,20,"êsi$, nek, ad afe$ iyi twaêesben"
  69,21,D$a ad yili di tudert igerzen
  69,22,di leonan aâlayen
  69,23,"Izwayen is, iwâa yasen"
  69,24,"àçet, teswem di lehna, ilmend n wayen tweqmem, ussan iâaddan"
  69,25,"Wanag win iwumi fkan tazmamt is, zelmev is, a d yini: \"a ssexv iw, awufan adlis iw ur d iusi"
  69,26,"Iqeîîiyen iw, ur éôi$ anwi"
  69,27,Awufan tameppant dayenni
  69,28,"Ayla w, ula iyi d ibbwi"
  69,29,"Adabu w, ipwakkes iyi\". ï"
  69,30,"Ïîfet ep, tarzem t"
  69,31,"D$a ar wu$ud, terrem t"
  69,32,"D$a s slesla n ûavet i$alen, teqqnem t"
  69,33,"Ih, illa ur iumin ara s Öebbi Ameqwôaêan"
  69,34,Ur ipnabi ar uceççi uéawali
  69,35,"Dagi, ur as illi, assa, uêbib"
  69,36,ne$ uççi siwa iôesvan
  69,37,Teppen ten kan imednuben
  69,38,"Ihi, ad Galle$ s wayen tepwalim"
  69,39,akked wayen ur tepwalim
  69,40,"ar wagi, s tidep, d awal Umazan ukyis"
  69,41,Ur illi d awal umedyaz; drus kan ay tumnem
  69,42,Ur illi d awal ugezzan; drus ay d tepmektayem
  69,43,D tarusi s$uô Mass imavalen
  69,44,Lemmer a d iskiddeb fella£ deg wawalen
  69,45,seg uyeffus ar at Neddem
  69,46,"d$a, aéaô n wul is, ad as Negzem"
  69,47,Ur ippili degwen w ara t ifukken
  69,48,"Neppa, ih, ar d asmekti i wid ipêezziben"
  69,49,"Neéôa, s tidep, ar llan garawen inekkaôen"
  69,50,"Neppa, ih, d tawa$it ijehliyen"
  69,51,"Neppa, ih, d tidep itebbtenÊ"
  69,52,Sbuccaâ isem n Mass ik Ameqwôaêan
  70,1,"Isteqsa yiwen, af uâaqeb iuran"
  70,2,i ijehliyen. Ur t ipxaûam yiwen
  70,3,"S$uô Öebbi, Bab n tseddaôin"
  70,4,"Lmalayek akked ôôuê, ppalin $uôeS, deg wass idumen smuset igima iseggwasen"
  70,5,"Ihi, eûbeô ûûebô ifazen"
  70,6,"Nitni, s tidep, walan t ibâad"
  70,7,Nwala t d aqôib
  70,8,"Asmi ara yili igenni, am uzzal ifsin"
  70,9,idurar ad ilin am tavuî
  70,10,Aêbib ur isteqsay aêbib
  70,11,"u mwalan. Ad ib$u ube$wvi, assen, ad isebbel tarwa s iwakken, seg uâaqeb, ad ipwafdu"
  70,12,"akked tmeîîut is, akked gma s"
  70,13,akked walag is it iûûôen
  70,14,akked wayen illan di tmurt meôôa; iwakken a t sellken
  70,15,"Xaîi, atan ujajiê"
  70,16,Isexxev agwlim
  70,17,"Issawel i win ixedâan, iaâûa"
  70,18,"ippadamen, ipsemmiden"
  70,19,"Amdan, s tidep, ipwaxleq d aêemmaq"
  70,20,"Ma innul it cceôô, atan di leqlala"
  70,21,"Ma innul it lxiô, ad isquceê"
  70,22,Kkes ed iméulla
  70,23,imezgiyen di téilla nnsen
  70,24,"i ippaken seg ayla nnsen, lêeqq ipwassnen"
  70,25,"i umappar, akked ume$bun"
  70,26,wid ipputebbten s wass iqeîîiyen
  70,27,wid iugaden aâaqeb n Mass nnsen
  70,28,"War ccekk, aâaqeb n Mass nnsen ur illi segs usellek"
  70,29,Wid iêurben af tuzzuft nnsen
  70,30,"kkes ed ar tilawin nnsen, ne$ piklatin nnsen; akka, ur ppulummun"
  70,31,"Wid ib$an sennig waya, widak d tilas ay zegren"
  70,32,"Wid ippaîîafen deg wawal nnsen, di tgallit nnsen"
  70,33,wid ippaîîafen di ccada nnsen
  70,34,wid ipêaraben $ef téilla nnsen
  70,35,"Widak, di leonanat, d imaâzuzen"
  70,36,"Acu iu$en ijehliyen, uzlen d $uôek, imegrav qquôen"
  70,37,"Yeffus, zelmev, d igrawen"
  70,38,"Yal amdan, segsen, issarem ad ikcem Loennet n ssaâd"
  70,39,"Xaîi! S tidep, Nxelq iten seg wayen éÈôan"
  70,40,"Ihi, ggulle$ s Mass igmav akked ituram, ar Nekwni d Wid izemren"
  70,41,"a d Nawi ay ten yifen, deg umkan nnsen! Ur a£ izeggwir yiwen"
  70,42,"Eoo iten ad slullven, ad uraren, ar d magren ass nnsen, win i sen ippuwaââden"
  70,43,"ass ideg ara d ff$en si tneîlin, ppazzalen, amzun ar id$a$en sbedden"
  70,44,"Ad brun i wallen, ddell fellasen. D wagi ay d ass i sen ippuwaââden"
  71,1,"S tidep, Nuzen ed Nuê i ugdud is: \"endeô agdud ik, uqbel a ten id ias uâaqeb aqeôêan"
  71,2,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Nek, i kunwi, d aneddaô ipbegginen"
  71,3,"Âabdet Öebbi, têezzbem aS, tessemêessem iyi"
  71,4,"Ad Isemmeê seg ibekkaven nnwen, ad awen Ifk lmudda ar lajel ipwassnen. S tidep, lajel n Öebbi, ma iusa d, ur ipwexxiô, lemmer peéôim"
  71,5,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Nek, ssawale$ i ugdud iw, am yiv am ass"
  71,6,Siwa tugin i sen terna ti$ôi w
  71,7,"Nek, yal tikelt ara ten neccde$ iwakken a sen Tsemmêev, ad rren ivudan nnsen deg imeééu$en nnsen, ad pplen deg iceîîiven nnsen. Ggernennen, zuxxen s tem$weô"
  71,8,"Sinna, ssawle$ asen s uâaggev"
  71,9,"Sinna, âinani nni$ asen; s tuffra, sser, mli$ assen"
  71,10,"Nni$: \"ssutret ssmaê i Mass nnwen; Neppa ard Win Ipsemmiêen"
  71,11,"Ippazen awen d ageffur, seg igenni, d ihedman"
  71,12,"Ayla akked tarwa, Issuget awen; Ifka yawen timizar; Irra yawen isaffen"
  71,13,"Acu kwen iu$en, Öebbi, ur aS tgim ccan"
  71,14,"Ni$ i waya, Ixelq ikwen"
  71,15,Ur twalam ara amek Ixleq Öebbi ûa igenwan d idurra
  71,16,"Irra degsen, aggur d tafat. Irra iîij d asavef"
  71,17,"Öebbi Issem$i kwen seg wakal, am im$an"
  71,18,"Sinna, a kwen Irr $uôes; sinna, d tuff$a ara kwen id Issuffe"
  71,19,Öebbi Irra yawen tamurt d tuwsiât
  71,20,"iwakken, degs, a ppafem iberdan d tiza"
  71,21,"Inna Nuê: \"a Mass iw! Atnan âuûan iyi. Ddan akked win iwumi, ayla s akked tarwa s, ay s rnan, siwa lexsaôa"
  71,22,Sxedmen tiêila meqqwôen
  71,23,"Nnan: \"ur ppaooat iôebbiten nnwen! Ur ppaooat Wadd, Suwaâ, Ya$ut, Yaâuq, akked Naûô"
  71,24,"Ni$ aîas ay telfen. Ur Trennuv i imednas, siwa ttelfan"
  71,25,"Ilmend n tuccva nnsen, $evûen, sinna kecmen ar tmes. War Öebbi, ur ppafen imâiwnen nnsen"
  71,26,"Inna Nuê: \"a Mass iw! Ur Ppaooa, seg ijehliyen, amezda$ di tmurt"
  71,27,"Aql aK id ma Teooiv ten, ad telfen imdanen iK. Siwa tijehli akked lâaô, ara d arwen"
  71,28,"A Mass iw, Semmeê a$, nek akked imawlan iw, akked win id ikecmen s axxam iw, iumen, akked wid d tid iumnen. Ur Rennu i imednas, siwa aquccu"
  72,1,"Ini: \"ippuweêêa yi d, ar agraw n leonun ssemêessen, u nnan: ih, nesla i Leqwôan, d lwehma"
  72,2,"Inehhu ar ûûwab, d$a numen yis. I Mass nne$, ur nepcarak yiwen"
  72,3,"U Neppa, gedha s loeôs n Mass nne$ Aâlayan, ur Isâi tameddakwelt, ne$ ùùmmi S"
  72,4,"Ih, abuhal nne$ iêekku, af Öebbi, ixmiôen"
  72,5,"Nekwni nenwa leonun akked imdanen, ur sawalen, af Öebbi, tikerkas, d awez$i"
  72,6,"Ih, seg imdanen, llan irgazen ijjemen ddkeô n leonun. Snernan lbe$wv nnsen"
  72,7,"S tidep, $ilen, akken t$ilem, ar Öebbi ur d Isskar yiwen, d awez$i"
  72,8,"Aql a$ nqelleb igenni, nufa t iççuô d iâssasen uqsiêen, akked ijujaê"
  72,9,"Nella nep$imi $uôes, seg imukan nessemêas; win issemêessen tura, a t id immager usafu d aâessas"
  72,10,"Nekwni, ur neéôi ma iura lhemm, af at ddunit, ne$ ma Ib$a, Mass nnsen, ad pwanhun"
  72,11,"Llan garane$ iâaôviyen, llan wid ur nemâin; ur naâdil iberdan"
  72,12,"Nmeyyez nufa, war ccekk, ur nesfunnug Öebbi di tmurt, ur T nesfunnug ma nerwel"
  72,13,"Nnhaya mi s nesla, yis numen. Win iumnen s Mass is, ur ippagwad ara t ixaûen, ne$ ara t ivuôôen"
  72,14,"Ih, garane$ imvuâen, garane$ lâaûûap. Wid iunzen, widak, xtaôen lewqam"
  72,15,"Ma d lâaûûap, di Loahennama, d nitni ay d is$aôen"
  72,16,"Lemmer deg ubrid ay ddan, yili Nefka yasen aman iqwan"
  72,17,"A ten njeôôeb yissen. Win iooan asmekti n Mass is, ad isâaddi aâaqeb aqesêan"
  72,18,Leowamaâ n Öebbi. Ur naâôet yiwen ar tama n Öebbi
  72,19,"Atan, mi ikker umdan n Öebbi ad inuj $ureS, qôib lesqen $uôes"
  72,20,"Ini: \"pnuju$ kan ar Mass iw, ur aS pcarake$ yiwen"
  72,21,"Ini: \"nek, ur pwakelfe$ $ef vveôô nnwen ne$ $ef nnhaya nnwen"
  72,22,"Ini: \"nek, ur iyi ipfukku yiwen seg ufus n Öebbi, d awez$i. War Neppa, ur ppafe$ ssôan"
  72,23,"siwa anabi s$uô Öebbi, akked tebrap iS\". Ih, i wid iâuûan Öebbi akked Umazan iS, times n Loahennama, ad wekkôen degs, i lebda"
  72,24,"Alamma mi walan ayen i sen ippuwaââden, ad éôen anwi ay d uôhifen mavi, i leslak, anwi drus iten mavi"
  72,25,"Ini: \"ur éôi$ ma iqeôb ed wayen i wen ippuweââden, ne$ ma a t Iweooel Mass iw"
  72,26,"Amusnaw n tbavnit; tabavnit iS, ur p Immal i yiwen"
  72,27,"Kkes ed win Iôuva d amazan. Winna, iteddu, zdat deffir, s iâssasen"
  72,28,"Ad Iéeô ma ssawven tibratin n Mass nnsen. Izzi i wayen akw illan $uôsen, Iêeppeb yal cci s imvanen"
  73,1,A win isburen
  73,2,"Aâwez, xas cwiî"
  73,3,"Azgen n yiv, ne$ ssenqes segs, acemma"
  73,4,Ne$ rnu yas. Di Leqwôan ûûun leqôaya
  73,5,"Aql a£, ad ak d Nini awal amray"
  73,6,"Ccaw n yiv, iééaéay kteô asurif, u issewqam kteô leqôaya"
  73,7,"Deg wass, s tidep, tce$wlev, maççi d kra"
  73,8,"Mmekti d isem n Mass ik, lhu yideS, akken iwata"
  73,9,"Mass ugmuv akked utaram, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, sâu T d Awkil"
  73,10,"Eûbeô i innan nnsen, faôeq iten s leêdaqa"
  73,11,"Eoo iyI inekkaôen, akked usâiyen; efk asen cwiî n lmudda"
  73,12,"£uône£, s tidep, slasel akked tmes iôeqqen"
  73,13,"lqut ipceôôiqen, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  73,14,"Ass ideg tamurt akked idurar ad rgagin, idurar ad u$alen am ôômel ippazalen"
  73,15,"Atan Nuzen awen ed Amazan, d anagi nnwen, akken Nuzen amazan i Ferâun"
  73,16,Ferâun iâuûa amazan. Newwet it tiyta tuqsiêt
